I'm trying to get my Vmware Workstation to use multiple monitors while running under i3.
When I try to activate more than one monitor in Workstation, it just informs me that the host windowsmanager (i3) does not support this.

After some googling, I found this: https://communities.vmware.com/thread/198341 which seems to indicate that the windowmanager has to support the hint
NETWM_FULLSCREEN_MONITORS
which, apparently i3wm does not.

Has anyone been able to find a workaround for this?
</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2015 08:49:06 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/6217/i3wm-vmware-workstation-multiple-monitors/</guid></item><item><title>Answer by ZaTTaZ for &lt;p&gt;Hi. 
